#
#
# build API - controlplane.base
# Use the --info flag to get build specific container image information.
#
# The build API consists of one method that builds the repository container image.
#
# build <repository selector>
# The build method without arguments builds the repository container image
# and tags the image with latest and the CONTECO_TAG.
#
# build --deep <repository selector>
# This _--deep_ flag force a recursive build of the base images recursively before building the container image.
#
#
